{"type":"text","timestamp":1775881523357,"sessionID":"ses_2853a130cffe7ZrnsNmL39pUlM","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac92fd8001lAe43qHHxy0Ptt","messageID":"msg_d7ac9278d001ATdWrYkBVULBeR","sessionID":"ses_2853a130cffe7ZrnsNmL39pUlM","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-018 — Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\n\n### Summary\n| Category | Status |\n|----------|--------|\n| **Module Implementation** | ✅ PASS |\n| **API Types** | ✅ PASS |\n| **Tests** | ✅ PASS (31 tests) |\n| **Build** | ✅ PASS |\n| **Code Quality** | ✅ PASS (`go vet` clean) |\n| **Client-Go Library** | ⚠️ NOT IMPLEMENTED (spec requirement) |\n\n---\n\n### 1. Module: `pkg/agentd` ✅\n\n**Files:**\n- `reconciler.go` (170 lines) - Main reconciler implementation\n- `reconciler_test.go` (931 lines) - Comprehensive test suite\n- `doc.go` (70 lines) - Package documentation\n\n**Implementation verified:**\n- ✅ `Reconciler` struct with `client.Client` and `*runtime.Scheme`\n- ✅ `Reconcile()` method implements idle cleanup logic:\n  - Fetches Sandbox by namespace/name\n  - Reads `last-activity-time` annotation\n  - Parses RFC3339 timestamp\n  - Deletes sandbox if expired (15 min timeout)\n  - Requeues at expiration time if not expired\n  - Handles NotFound errors gracefully (idempotent)\n- ✅ `SetupWithManager()` registers controller to watch Sandbox resources\n- ✅ Constants: `SessionExpirationTimeout` (15m), `RequeueAfterParseError` (30s)\n\n**Tests (31 tests, all passing):**\n- Core reconciliation flow (NotFound, GetError, NoAnnotation, etc.)\n- Timestamp parsing (valid RFC3339, malformed, empty)\n- Expiration logic (not expired, just expired, expired)\n- Delete operations (NotFound, error, success)\n- Edge cases (context cancellation, multiple namespaces, far future, zero time)\n- Benchmark test included\n\n---\n\n### 2. API Types ✅\n\n**Package:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n| Type | Resource | Status |\n|------|----------|--------|\n| `AgentRuntime` | `agentruntimes` | ✅ Defined with kubebuilder markers |\n| `AgentRuntimeList` | - | ✅ Defined |\n| `CodeInterpreter` | `codeinterpreters` | ✅ Defined with kubebuilder markers |\n| `CodeInterpreterList` | - | ✅ Defined |\n| `Sandbox` | `sandboxes` | ✅ Defined with kubebuilder markers |\n| `SandboxList` | - | ✅ Defined |\n\n**SchemeGroupVersion:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` ✅\n\n---\n\n### 3. Integration with Workload Manager ✅\n\n**Annotation Key:** `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"last-activity-time\"`\n- Used by reconciler to read activity timestamp\n- Test verifies expected value\n\n---\n\n### 4. Client-Go Library ⚠️ NOT IMPLEMENTED\n\n**Spec Requirement:** Generated Kubernetes client code for API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n**Missing:**\n- ❌ `client-go/` directory\n- ❌ Clientset with Interface\n- ❌ Typed client for runtime/v1alpha1\n- ❌ AgentRuntimes/CodeInterpreters interfaces\n- ❌ Fake clients\n- ❌ Informers\n- ❌ Listers\n- ❌ Code generation script (`hack/update-codegen.sh`)\n\n**Note:** The client-go library is typically auto-generated using `k8s.io/code-generator`. The API types are properly defined with `+genclient` markers, enabling future generation.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Issues Found\n\n| Issue | Severity | Description |\n|-------|----------|-------------|\n| Duplicate constant | Low | `router.LastActivityAnnotationKey` (\"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\") differs from `workloadmanager.LastActivityAnnotationKey` (\"last-activity-time\"). The router constant is unused. |\n\n---\n\n### 6. Test Results\n\n```bash\n$ go test ./pkg/agentd/... -v\n=== RUN   TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound\n--- PASS: TestReconcile_SandboxNotFound (0.00s)\n... (31 tests total)\nPASS\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd    0.017s\n\n$ go test ./pkg/apis/... -v\n... (all tests pass)\nPASS\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1    0.010s\n```\n\n---\n\n### 7. Conclusion\n\n**AR-018 (Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller):** ✅ **IMPLEMENTED AND VERIFIED**\n\nThe reconciler implementation correctly:\n- Watches Sandbox resources\n- Reads the `last-activity-time` annotation\n- Deletes sandboxes that have been idle beyond 15 minutes\n- Handles all error cases gracefully\n- Is fully tested with 31 test cases\n\n**Client-Go Library:** ⚠️ **NOT IMPLEMENTED** (separate from AR-018 scope)\n\nThe API types are properly defined and ready for client generation, but the generated client-go code described in the spec is not present. This would typically be generated using Kubernetes code-generator tools.","time":{"start":1775881523353,"end":1775881523353}}}
